==English==
===Etymology===
From [[frightening]] + [[-ly]]
===Adverb===
'''frighteningly'''

# In a [[frightening]] or [[terrifying]] manner.
# [[very|Very]]; beyond [[usual]] expectation so as to cause [[surprise]] or [[concern]].
#:''The pitcher that was set before me was '''frighteningly''' large.''

